  "texts": [
    "Students who understand the underlying mechanisms and potential biases of AI systems can critically evaluate the responses provided by ChatGPT (Huber et al., 2024).",
    "Therefore, gaining AI literacy and effective prompt writing skills can support better decision-making, reduce the risk of relying on faulty information and promote responsible use of AI (Knoth et al., 2024).",
    "Guided practice and scaffolding can also be essential components of effective AI integration in courses.",
    "Guided practice can involve structured learning activities where students can explore and apply fundamental concepts with the support of AI (Foung et al., 2024).",
    "During these activities, instructors can provide step-by-step instructions or model how to effectively interact with the AI, including how to craft precise and relevant prompts (Darvishi et al., 2024)."
  ],
